and blessings be upon him, while his companions were numerous, we preferred Abu Bakr, Umar, and Uthman, then we would remain silent. Source: Musnad Ah\u0323mad 4626 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Arna\u2019ut Imam Ahmad commented, \u201cThe best of\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":33240,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/08\/19\/hasan-ahl-al-sunnah-gentle\/","url_meta":{"origin":35032,"position":1},"title":"Hasan on Sunnah: O people of Sunnah, be gentle with each other","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 19, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Mubarak reported: Al-Hasan al-Basri, may Allah have mercy on him, said, \u201cO followers of the Sunnah! Be gentle with each other, may Allah have mercy on you, for you are surely in the minority of people.\u201d Source: Sharh\u0323 Us\u0323u\u0304l I\u02bbtiqa\u0304d Ahl al-Sunnah 15 \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0645\u064f\u0628\u064e\u0627\u0631\u064e\u0643\u064d \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0652\u062d\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0646\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0635\u0631\u064a \u0631\u062d\u0645\u0647 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":17079,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/12\/02\/awzai-sunnah-hadith-careful\/","url_meta":{"origin":35032,"position":2},"title":"Awza\u2019i on Sunnah: Be careful not to contradict the Prophet","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 2, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"'Amir ibn Yasaf reported: Al-Awza\u2019i, may Allah have mercy on him, said, \u201cO 'Amir, if a tradition reaches you from the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon, beware not to say differently. Verily, the Prophet conveyed from Allah Almighty.\u201d Source: al-Madkhal ila\u0304 al-Sunan al-Kubra\u0301 173 \u0639\u0646 \u0639\u064e\u0627\u0645\u0650\u0631 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":2787,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/04\/06\/wudu-perfect-ablution\/","url_meta":{"origin":35032,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Wudu: Description of a perfect ablution","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 6, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Humran reported: Uthman, may Allah be pleased with him, requested a vessel of water and he poured water over his hands three times and washed them. Then, he put his right hand in the vessel and rinsed his mouth and sniffed water into his nose. Then, he washed his face\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":20746,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2015\/07\/06\/family-body-rights\/","url_meta":{"origin":35032,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Rights: Your family and own body has rights over you","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 6, 2015","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, sent for Uthman ibn Mazh\u2019un and he came. The Prophet said, \u201cO Uthman, do you not desire my practice?\u201d Uthman said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, no by Allah. I seek your practice.\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cVerily, I sleep and I\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":26300,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2018\/04\/29\/enjoin-goodness-women-family\/","url_meta":{"origin":35032,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Marriage: Encouragement to stay married in old age","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 29, 2018","format":false,"excerpt":"Al-Miqdam ibn Ma\u2019di reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, stood up for the people and praised Allah as is due to Him, saying, \u201cVerily, Allah instructs you to treat women well, and again, Allah instructs you to treat women well, for they are your mothers,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/35032","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/3712"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-js